episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Comedians Dai Henwood, Tom Sainsbury, Kura Turawhenua and Nina Oyama answer an array of spelling questions. These include The Gift of Spelling, Spell the Crime, Do the Time and Homophones.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Guests this week include Robbie Nicol, Justine Smith and Pax Assadi plus our mystery winner from episode one. The challenges this week inclue The Hat Hat, Horsing: A Round and Spell the Smell.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Rose Matafeo, Eli Matthewson, Becky Umbers and our victorious episode two winner battle it out with a vast array of spelling games.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Rhys Mathewson, Liv McKenzie, Itay Dom and our mighty winner from episode three join Guy Montgomery for a bunch of spelling tasks

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Maria Williams, Jason Hoyte, Julia Morris and our famous episode four winner tackle Guy Montgomery and his wordy challenges.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Episode six follows Jono Pryor, Paul Douglas, Kalyani Nagarajan and our episode five champion on to the stage to answer Guy Montgomery's spelling tasks.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: In this episode Ben Hurley, Rhiannon McCall, Jacquie Brown and our reigning champ from episode four try to take each other down with their varied spelling knowledge.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: In our final episode Joe Daymond, Janaye Henry, Paul Ego and our winning player from episode seven fight to the very spelling death to be named winner of Guy Mont's Spelling Bee!
